node.text:
🎉 JUNETEENTH G I V E A W A Y 🎉

I’ve teamed up with @sweetmaescookieco for a sweet giveaway in honor of Juneteenth! The rules are simple! 
⭐️ Follow me & @sweetmaescookieco 
⭐️ Tag 2 friends in the comments below 
The winner will be announced on @sweetmaescookieco IG Sunday! 

Sweet Mae’s Cookie Co is a black-woman owned cookie company. Sweet Mae’s is a premium stuffed cookie company with a southern accent. What is unique about their cookies is they are all made with brown butter and stuffed. Their cookies are thick and filled with delicious fillings such as Nutella, Cookie Butter, Cream Cheese and more. Their flavors come from desserts you see in the south like Carrot Cake and Red Velvet or things their Founder, Tiffany, grew up eating in her childhood. Sweet Mae’s was started from Tiffany’s passion of baking and a way to express that passion through each cookie she bakes!
